    {
        "content": "<p>I go with the title, \"proof by computation\" would be</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">helpMe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">padWithO</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"abc\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"ooabc\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">native_decide</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>But <code>native_decide</code> can be considered dangerous in some context, so please wait for a better answer by someone else</p>",
        "id": 564592229,
        "sender_full_name": "Weiyi Wang",
        "timestamp": 1766103559
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Oh, this works</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">helpMe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">padWithO</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"abc\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"ooabc\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">decide</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 564592386,
        "sender_full_name": "Weiyi Wang",
        "timestamp": 1766103633
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Oh, interesting, <code>decide +kernel</code> fails on <a href=\"https://live.lean-lang.org/#project=mathlib-v4.24.0&amp;\">v24</a> but succeeds on Latest. Looks like we gained some Decidable instances recently.</p>",
        "id": 564592802,
        "sender_full_name": "Li Xuanji",
        "timestamp": 1766103815
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Note that if you add <code>@[reducible]</code> to the def then decide works on its own.</p>\n<p>Without that you can also do </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">helpMe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">padWithO</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"abc\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"ooabc\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">with_unfolding_all</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">decide</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
